REST API Parameter Reference

api_parameter_reference

Format

A tibble dataframe

method

Geocoder service shortname

generic_name

Generic name of the API parameter

api_name

Name of the parameter for the geocoder service specified in the method field

default_value

Default value of this parameter

required

Is the parameter required by the API?

Source

  • LocationIQ (IQ)

  • Nominatim (OSM)

  • Census

  • Geocodio
